      <title>洛杉矶港 5 月份进口下降 4.5%，出口增长 23.8%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/port-of-los-angeles-imports-fell-4-5-in-may-exports-rose-23-8</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2024 年前五个月，洛杉矶港的进口量尽管 5 月份与去年同期相比有所下降，但仍高于疫情前的峰值。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/port-of-los-angeles-imports-fell-4-5-in-may-exports-rose-23-8</guid>
