    <item>
      <title>玻利维亚在燃料短缺的情况下向加油站部署军队</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/bolivia-deploys-military-to-gas-stations-amid-fuel-shortage</link>
      <description><![CDATA[玻利维亚正在派遣军队前往加油站，以遏制补贴燃料的走私，据政府称，走私补贴燃料导致全国范围内的汽油和柴油短缺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/bolivia-deploys-military-to-gas-stations-amid-fuel-shortage</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 23:07:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国顾问称美国对华出口限制损害两国利益</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/us-s-china-export-limits-hurt-both-nations-china-advisor-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[著名学者、北京政治顾问机构常务委员贾庆国表示，美国限制对华关键技术出口的举措正在损害两国经济，并可能适得其反。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/us-s-china-export-limits-hurt-both-nations-china-advisor-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 23:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍勃·梅内德斯利用检察官的工作面试为朋友游说</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/bob-menendez-used-prosecutor-s-job-interview-to-lobby-for-friend</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名新泽西州的律师在 2021 年成为该州最高联邦检察官，他作证说，参议员鲍勃·梅嫩德斯 (Bob Menendez) 在一次工作面试中告诉他，一位朋友被“不公平地”起诉，如果他得到这个职位，他应该仔细审查这个案件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/bob-menendez-used-prosecutor-s-job-interview-to-lobby-for-friend</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 22:35:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>如果美联储设定错误的通胀率目标，将酿成“悲剧”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/federal-reserve-inflation-interest-rate-policy-tied-to-new-zealand-experiment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今日热点：20 世纪 90 年代新西兰的试验与美联储维持利率在近期高位之间的联系 — — 以及为什么这可能是一个错误。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/federal-reserve-inflation-interest-rate-policy-tied-to-new-zealand-experiment</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 22:12:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国警告称，俄罗斯引领对手试图影响 2024 年大选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/russia-leads-adversaries-looking-to-sway-vote-us-officials-warn</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国官员周三表示，以俄罗斯为首的越来越多的美国对手正寻求通过雇佣商业公司和使用生成人工智能来影响 2024 年总统大选。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/russia-leads-adversaries-looking-to-sway-vote-us-officials-warn</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 22:01:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿根廷推动新计划期间米莱将与国际货币基金组织总裁会面</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/milei-to-meet-imf-chief-amid-argentina-s-push-for-new-program</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷总统哈维尔·米莱本周将在意大利与国际货币基金组织总裁举行会谈，阿根廷声称其在寻求新资金以最终取消资本管制方面已经扫清了一个关键障碍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/milei-to-meet-imf-chief-amid-argentina-s-push-for-new-program</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 19:54:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯塔默誓言工党将重点关注财富创造，以削弱保守党</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/starmer-promises-labour-focus-on-wealth-creation-to-blunt-tories</link>
      <description><![CDATA[基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 表示，他将把经济增长和创造财富作为工党宣言的核心，他的民意调查领先反对党试图在 7 月 4 日英国大选之前削弱保守党在税收方面的攻击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/starmer-promises-labour-focus-on-wealth-creation-to-blunt-tories</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 19:42:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>米莱的改革方案在参议院首次关键投票中勉强通过</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/milei-s-signature-reforms-at-risk-in-tense-argentine-senate-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统哈维尔·米莱签署的改革方案在阿根廷参议院勉强获得初步批准，但其最重要的财政措施在逐项投票中面临强烈反对。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/milei-s-signature-reforms-at-risk-in-tense-argentine-senate-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 15:57:35 GMT</pubDate>
